    <div id="about-me">
        <h1 id="about">ABOUT</h1>
        <hr style="color:black; font-size:50px;">

        <br>
        <h2>Welcome to my portfolio where I try to show the world a bit about myself</h2>
        <br>
        <h4>(Hover over the images and learn something about myself)</h4>
        <br>
        <div class="rest">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <ul class="flag about-cards effect">
                        <li>
                            <figure>

                                <%=image_tag("flag2.jpg", class:"top") %>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <h2>+254 is my Land!</h2>
                                    <p>I am a proud citizen of Kenya.</p>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <ul class="computer about-cards effect">
                        <li>
                            <figure>

                                <%=image_tag("backlit.jpg", class:"top") %>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <h2>Software development is my speciality</h2>
                                    <p>Just like King Arthur and his sword, I knew software development would be my life from the moment i lay my eyes on a keyboard.It was destiny you could say</p>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <ul class="gear about-cards effect">
                        <li>
                            <figure>

                                <%=image_tag("gear.jpg", class:"top") %>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <h2>Cars are my passion</h2>
                                    <p>When i'm not busy punching characters, you'll find me tinkering under the hood of cars or watching reruns of Top Gear as i marvel at the wonderful inventions of man in the automibile industry.</p>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-4">
                    <ul class="rugby about-cards effect">
                        <li>
                            <figure>
                                <%=image_tag("rugby1.jpg", class:"ruby") %>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <h2>Avid rugby fan</h2>
                                    <p>My oh my, what a wonderful sport.The effort and strategy that goes into scoring a try is what I love the most
                                    </p>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-4">
                    <ul class="food about-cards effect">
                        <li>
                            <figure>

                                <%=image_tag("food.jpg", class:"top") %>
                                <figcaption>
                                    <h2>Feed me and I'll tell you more.</h2>
                                    <p>Well there is so much to tell and too little a space but feed me and i could tell you more.Ps food is the way to my heart</p>
                                </figcaption>
                            </figure>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- <hr width="50%" size="8" align="center"> -->
        <hr style="color:black; font-size:50px;">

        <h1 id="about">PORTFOLIO</h1>

        <hr style="color:black; font-size:50px;">
        <h2>This are the skills I have been able to aquire thus far.</h2>
          <h2>In them are some of the projects I have worked on using the language listed:</h2>

        <div id="skills">
            <ul>
              <div class="row">

                <% @skills.each do |skill|%>

                <div class="col-md-4 skill-images">
                  <li><%= link_to skill_path(skill) do%><%= image_tag(skill.image.url(:medium))%>
                    <h3><strong><%=skill.language%></strong></h3>
                    <% end %>
                  </li>
                </div>
                <%end%>
              </div>
            </ul>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <p><%= link_to "Add language", new_skill_path %></p>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
